#10200
Name:	Senator's Holding Pen
Desc:$
   This is the Initiation Quest Zone by Stealth. Here are the instructions
(proposed, do what you want really but this kinda follows the real game
mechanics): You will need to medit the various mobs. You need to edit their
stats to match the stats of the player's astral reflection or to a level equal
to the level of initiation+1 (ex: level 1 initiations use mobs with stats of
6, level 2 initiations use stats of 7, etc). They are already set to be
sentinels, so they will not wander once loaded. Load the Dweller to room
10202, 'You' to room 10203 (or to the holding pen at room 10200 (here), if you
want the mob to make an appearance). The 4 elemental mobs should be loaded to
room 10205 and then can be switched into and moved to there respective rooms
as needed.
   The rules are pretty simple. Teleport the player's astral reflection to
10201. Once he gets to the dweller, ask if he is ready (using zecho, or by
standing there invisible). If so, teleport him to 10203 and have him fight his
double (the 'You' mob). Once done there, teleport him to 10204 and ask him to
choose a plane to start his quest. Teleport him to the plane and then bring in
the appropriate mob. Once he defeats that mob, ask and teleport him to his
next choice. When all 4 planes are conquered, teleport him to 10210 and
'INITIATE' to the correct level.
   Astral players on the Metaplanes can be wounded and die. Monitor the
player's astral form and 'set' his player to the appropriate damage levels. If
his persona gets KO'd, force it to return and set the player Ment to 0. If the
persona is killed, kill the player as well. He will be able to start another
quest after 1 MUD hour.
   If the player returns voluntarily (ie attempting to cheat death), allow him
to but he will be penalized by not being allowed to initiate for 28 MUD days
(post a notice  with the date after which he can initiate again to the quest
board).
   That's about it, hope this is helpful. 
~
