#10201
Name:	Speeding along the Ether
Desc:$
   You are used to the astral plane and its metaphors and symbolism, where you
move as fast as thought. But now, you travel as if at speeds unimagined
through the ether. Other worlds fly by as you accelerate from your home plane.
Worlds unrecognizable, with being new to your mind. They are there but for a
moment's time and then gone as you continue to rush towards your destination.
You know you are traveling to a place outside time and space, above thought
and desire, beyond comprehension... 
~
