#10202
Name:	The Threshold
Desc:$
   Just as your feeble intellect begins to attempt to understand all that you
have seen, you come to an abrupt halt. You hang in a void. You are momentarily
disoriented and thoughless as you hover in the nothing of it. Then you notice
small stars in the distance. You see your own tiny silvery thread of life
stretched back to one of these stars. Suddenly you realize these are not
stars, but planes of existance. Each another reality to be explored and
experienced. But as soon as this realization comes to you, you note a dark
entity coalesce before you. 
~
