#10204
Name:	A Barren Plane
Desc:$
   The mirrored sphere shatters into a million reflective shards, each
spinning off into the distance carrying an image of you. You shield your eyes
from the needles of glass. Lowering your hand, you stand upon a flat
featureless plain, stretching unremarkably to the limits of your perception.
The ground beneath your feet feels strange and spongy. Examining it, you
realize it is more like flesh than earth, yielding and warm to your touch. You
notice movement in the sky above you. Spinning chaotically in contention with
one another are four spheres. A searing ball of flame, a hugh metallic meteor,
an undulating glob of liquid and a amorpheous mass of clouds. They fly and
dodge about one another, each seeking some dominant position, constantly in
motion. A voice whispers to you, as if from afar, "^rThis is the plane of the
Material, for whence all comes. Above you war the four elemental planes of
your existance: Fire, Earth, Water and Air. You must prove your worth by
conquering the challenges of each. A true mage controls these forces and to
pass your quest, you must do so. This is the place of Choosing, from here you
shall never return once you once you have chosen your path. Name the first
step on your journey and look not back!^N" 
~
