#10206
Name:	A Swirling Conflagration
Desc:$
   ^rSearing heat blasts you from every direction! You hang in the midest of a
chaotic, everchanging world of flame. Your very lungs scream as you attempt to
breath the noxious burning fumes that seem to be the very substance of this
place. There is no solid mass to call earth here, just an all consuming
conflagration, as if you hung in the middle of the Sun. You do notice what
seems to be movement within this sea of fire. You begin to see balls of flame
and small lizard-like animals wreathed in glowing plasma, darting about. Some
have turned there attention to you.^N 
~
