#10207
Name:	A Deep Green Sea
Desc:$
   ^GYou float within a deep green mass of water, reminding of you of the times
you went diving in the Seattle Bay. Strangely, your lungs fill with the fuild
around you yet do not cry out of air. You feel as comfortable as if you were
back in the womb before your birth. You notice an abundance of life swimming
here, some you recognize, others are strange yet still beautiful. As you
remain mesmerized by the teeming world before you, you are abruptly brought
back to the reality of where you are. You float, suddenly aghast, as you watch
larger predatory creature ruthlessly devour their smaller cousins. You also
begin notice strange eddies in the calm waters, moving purposely. These eddies
begin to take vaguely humaniod shape, still fluid and changing, yet
coagulating into gigantic entities filled will malevolent intellect. Some turn
their attention to you.^N 
~
