#10209
Name:	A Metallic Meteor
Desc:$
   ^LYou find yourself standing on a rough plain of igneous rock, huge shining
metal crystals jut up through the stone, towering above you. The ground shakes
and rumbles as geysers of molten rock erupt around you, showering the area
with ash and searing stone fragments. The very ground convulses and
convolutes, as if engaged in some titanic struggle with itself. The earth
directly before you suddenly cracks and splits, dropping off into nothingness,
leaving a gaping chasm just inches from your feet. Within this new gulf you
see movement. A gigantic being of stone and rock climbs up from this abyss,
towards you.^N 
~
