Desc:$
   You stand upon a flat featureless plain, stretching unremarkably to the
limits of your perception. The ground beneath your feet feels strange and
spongy. Examining it, you realize it is more like flesh than earth, yielding
and warm to your touch. You notice movement in the sky above you. Orbiting one
another in an orderly fashion are four spheres. A searing ball of flame, a
hugh metallic meteor, an undulating glob of liquid and a amorpheous mass of
clouds. These four elements rotate in perfect harmony with one another,
encircling you, as if you are their Sun, their center. A voice whispers to
you, as if from afar, "This is the plane of the Material, for whence all
comes. Above you orbit the four elemental planes of your existance: Fire,
Earth, Water and Air. You have tamed these planes and made their power yours.
You control them to do your bidding and fulfill your desires. You have
accomplished your quest and may now enter the Citadel to claim your prize." 
~
